cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper deals with computer vision and robotics, specifically in the context of road marking segmentation. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the use of domain randomization, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). Additionally, the paper uses deep learning techniques, which could fall under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper deals with road layouts, which could fall under the category of graphics (cs.GR).
